<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h2 style="color: #333333;">Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555555;">Your OTP code is:</p>
        <h1 style="font-size: 36px; color: #333333; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 4px;"><%= otp %></h1>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555555;">Please use this code to complete your transaction. The code is valid for the next 30 minutes.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555555;">If you did not request this code, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555555;">Thank you,</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555555;">The Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
